

A Machine Learning-based web app built using Streamlit to detect fraudulent credit card transactions.

* Features
- Predicts whether a transaction is **Fraud** or **Normal**
- Built using **Random Forest Classifier**
- Interactive UI with Streamlit
- Sample data buttons for quick testing

* Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas, NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Streamlit

* Project Structure
fraud-detection/
│
├── app/
│ └── app.py # Streamlit app
│
├── model/
│ └── train_model.py # Model training script
│
├── data/ # Dataset (ignored in Git)
│
├── model.pkl # Trained model (ignored in Git)
├── .gitignore
└── README.md

* Setup Instructions

